headline: Northern Trust Launches Fixed Income ETF Suites
summary: CHICAGO, August 19, 2025--Northern Trust Asset Management has launched three suites of fixed income ETFs today. The 11 new ETFs are the first funds under the new Northern Trust ETFs brand.
